From 5b941bd141785949a212f1500b2364d6cec6432d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 18 Jul 2025 17:10:03 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Refactor HAL TLV Parsing APIs

Currently, compact TLVs are parsed using hal monitor ops and the parsed
data are populated into the ppdu_info structure via the common function
ath12k_wifi7_hal_mon_rx_parse_status_tlv().

This change refactors the TLV parsing logic by delegating the parsing and
ppdu_info updates to corresponding HAL-specific functions.

Patch-dependency:
	0406-0001-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Enable-word-mask-subscriptio.patch

Signed-off-by: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
